=begin pod

=head1 NAME

C<Geo::Location> - Provides location data for astronomical and other programs

=head1 SYNOPSIS

=begin code :lang<raku>
$ raku
> use Geo::Location;
> my $loc = Location.new;
> say $loc.name;
Gulf Breeze, FL, USA
> say $loc.location;
lat: 30.485092, lon: -86.4376157
=end code

=head1 DESCRIPTION

B<Geo::Location> Provides location data for
astronomical and other programs.

